      "path": "/books/nahj-al-balagha:3:167:1",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/32/3/264/321",
      "text": [
        "٢٦٤. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): أَحْسِنُوا فِي عَقِبِ غَيْرِكُمْ تُحْفَظُوا فِي عَقِبِكُمْ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "264. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: Do good with the bereaved ones of others so that good is done to your bereaved ones also."
        ]
      }
    }
